        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Activation:</strong> <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"Special Activation\" aria-label=\"Special Activation\">*</span></p><p><em>You set an example from the front, applying your advice to your own actions.</em></p><p>Before you make an <strong>Athletics</strong>, <strong>Agility</strong>, or <strong>Leadership</strong> test, you can spend 1 focus to roll your command die and add the result to your d20 roll.</p><p>Additionally, when you acquire this talent, increase the size of your command die by one size (such as from a d4 to a d6).</p>",
            "chat": "<p><strong>Activation:</strong> <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"Special Activation\" aria-label=\"Special Activation\">*</span></p><p>Increase the size of your command die. Spend 1 focus to add your command die to your <strong>Athletic</strong>, <strong>Agility</strong>, or <strong>Leadership</strong> d20 roll.</p>",
            "short": "<p><strong>Activation:</strong> <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"Special Activation\" aria-label=\"Special Activation\">*</span></p><p>Before you make an <strong>Athletics</strong>, <strong>Agility</strong>, or <strong>Leadership</strong> test, you can spend 1 focus to roll your command die and add the result to your d20 roll.</p><p>Additionally, when you acquire this talent, increase the size of your command die by one size (such as from a d4 to a d6).</p>"
